PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782145126
OL,3,CExtreme heat warnings issued as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to exceed 35C during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FThis intense heatwave will have a
OL,8,Fdifferent feel to the 40C heatwave in
OL,9,FJuly 2022 - it's forecast to have much
OL,10,Fhigher humidity adding to the
OL,11,Fdiscomfort and at this stage is
OL,12,Fforecast to last longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
